<br>
These &quot;subjugated races&quot; are in the thrall of the (for lack of a better word) villains in the game. Find a way to free them and they become a PC race. They haven't release the names of these other races yet. <br>
<br>
On the upside -- imagine a server sort of unifying together to free this race. Feels like an RP opportunity (even if the reason is &quot;I wanna play a new creature!!!&quot;) and a chance for a whole server to have a sense of accomplishment. <br>
