<br>
I am beginning to see that there will likely be a good distribution among the classes.  For a few months after release, there will likely be a lot of people playing dragons, but many of them will change when they see the accomplishments of other races.<br>
<br>
My personal beef with dragons?  They look the same for the entire game.  They have inventory, and can craft scales that increase their base stats, but no graphics.  There are two stages of size increasing, each of which will be akin to an epic quest in EQ, from what has been said.  So an ancient dragon is very impressive sight.  But don't count on getting close to the first size increase unless you are a hardcore player.<br>
<br>
Dragons can craft their own lairs, that's neat.<br>
